   857Ôćĺ#### `P._` wildcard
   859ÔćĺThe `P._` pattern will match any value. You can also use `P.any`, which is an alias to `P._`.
   860Ôćĺ
   861Ôćĺ```ts
   862Ôćĺimport { match, P } from 'ts-pattern';
   863Ôćĺ
   864Ôćĺconst input = 'hello';
   865Ôćĺ
