     7Ôćĺ## TypeScript v5
     9ÔćĺBecause it relies on [const type parameters](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-5-0.html#const-type-parameters), TS-Pattern v5 requires TypeScript v5+!
